---
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use functional components with TypeScript only
- Use named exports over default exports
- All forms must use react-hook-form with Zod validation
- Use React Query for data fetching, never raw useEffect
- Keep components under 200 lines; extract logic to custom hooks
- Always use Tailwind CSS for styling, no inline styles
- Implement accessibility: aria-label, tabIndex, keyboard handlers
- Use early returns to reduce nesting
- AbortController for all async useEffect cleanup
